#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""htmlq reimplementation in pure Python stdlib.

Approximates htmlq 0.4.0 (https://github.com/mgdm/htmlq) behavior:
HTML5 parsing, CSS selector matching, html5ever-style serialization.
